@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> IDLE

IDLE --> TRACKING : Object gedetecteerd
TRACKING --> PREDICTING : voldoende samples
PREDICTING --> MOVING_TO_TARGET : haalbaar landpunt
MOVING_TO_TARGET --> CATCHING : object dichtbij target
CATCHING --> RECOVERY : Object opgevangen
RECOVERY --> IDLE : Reset klaar

TRACKING --> IDLE : object verloren
MOVING_TO_TARGET --> IDLE : Timeout

@enduml
